title: Define Project Requirements
description: Create a detailed list of project requirements for ThoughtControlledRobotic based on the BCI system and space exploration context.

title: Design BCI System Architecture
description: Create a high-level design for the BCI system that will be used to control the robotic systems.

title: Develop Robotic System Architecture
description: Design the overall architecture for the robotic system that will be controlled by the BCI.

title: Develop BCI System Software
description: Write the software for the BCI system that will interpret brain signals and translate them into commands for the robotic system.

title: Develop Robotic System Software
description: Write the software for the robotic system that will receive commands from the BCI and execute them.

title: Test BCI System Integration
description: Perform integration testing to ensure that the BCI and robotic systems are working together as intended.

title: Integrate BCI and Robotic Systems for Space Exploration
description: Combine the BCI system and robotic systems to create a solution suitable for space exploration.
